OL,5, P&O Ferries' sacking of 800 staff      
OL,6, without warning last week was "awful"  
OL,7, and "wrong", Chancellor Rishi Sunak has
OL,8, told the BBC.                          
OL,10,FThe government is examining the        
OL,11,Flegality of the firm's actions, the    
OL,12,Fchancellor confirmed.                  
OL,14,FHowever, the Sunday Times reports that 
OL,15,Fministers knew of the plan to sack crew
OL,16,Fbeforehand, but failed to challenge it.
OL,18,FThe Department for Transport said "full
OL,19,Fdetails" were not available at that    
OL,20,Fstage.                                 
